{"tid":981179,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"他得絕症 迪士尼讓他先看《復仇4》","createTime":"2019-01-14T05:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-18T19:15:54.000Z","uid":212399,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c636f0799828ca66d8581cbd202dc3b2362de060","tid":981179,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:50:26.000Z","msg":"國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n漫威宇宙電影《復仇者聯盟》擁有不少死忠粉絲，最新的一集《復仇者聯盟4：終局之戰》即將在今年4月上映，不過在澳洲有一名影迷因為癌症身體狀況每況愈下，擔心自己沒辦法撐到最新一集上映，上網抒發情緒，沒想到迪士尼公司真的幫助他圓夢，答應讓他成為全球首位看到續集的影迷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.ZQEGtXDUblf9dIPN7hzgg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUyNy4wNTg4MjM1Mjk0MTE3/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/yLq5kSCCcjYOv5yis5lfKg--~B/aD00MjA7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/b697212352a013ebd8f358246c289b1a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F.ZQEGtXDUblf9dIPN7hzgg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTUyNy4wNTg4MjM1Mjk0MTE3%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FyLq5kSCCcjYOv5yis5lfKg--~B%2FaD00MjA7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2Fb697212352a013ebd8f358246c289b1a&h=5766084e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲漫威迷得絕症迪士尼佛心決定讓他先看最新一集的復仇者聯盟。(圖／翻攝自UNILAD)<br />\n根據外電媒體報導，這名在澳洲今年33歲的男子亞歷山大因為罹患罕見疾病「范可尼氏貧血」，引發肝癌、口腔癌和骨髓衰竭等多種癌症，身為漫威迷的他，擔心自己沒辦法撐到今年4月電影上映，因此上網抒發心情。<br />\n他在論壇「Reddit」上抒發心情，表示自己從小就是漫威迷，從未錯過任何一部系列電影，但因為癌症化療，很有可能在今年4月就要迎接自己的「Endgame」，擔心自己離開後不僅看不到最新一部電影，還得留下女友離開人世。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/Bxe0B6mb3Yl.EtYbVd9uow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTYyNC45NDExNzY0NzA1ODgz/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/6uZwLfyXzGgWz74eJnQm7Q--~B/aD00OTg7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/c81174535269933883dc8e58d269cf92\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FBxe0B6mb3Yl.EtYbVd9uow--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTY0MDtoPTYyNC45NDExNzY0NzA1ODgz%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F6uZwLfyXzGgWz74eJnQm7Q--~B%2FaD00OTg7dz01MTA7c209MTthcHBpZD15dGFjaHlvbg--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2Fc81174535269933883dc8e58d269cf92&h=cfb82540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲漫威迷得絕症迪士尼佛心決定讓他先看最新一集的復仇者聯盟。(圖／翻攝自Reddit)<br />\n結果這篇文章被女友和網友熱心轉載，還有網友設計海報跟影片幫忙宣傳，果真被迪士尼公司看到，主動連繫他，看要如何讓他先看到《復仇者聯盟4》。<br />\n（編輯：馮珮汶）<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/他得絕症-迪士尼讓他先看-復聯4-000504172.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fcelebrity%2F%E4%BB%96%E5%BE%97%E7%B5%95%E7%97%87-%E8%BF%AA%E5%A3%AB%E5%B0%BC%E8%AE%93%E4%BB%96%E5%85%88%E7%9C%8B-%E5%BE%A9%E8%81%AF4-000504172.html&d=v0UtrIthVh3L%2FppYQHlmQh4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=de49a562\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/celebrity/他得絕症-迪士尼讓他先看-復聯4-000504172.html</a>"},{"pid":"f94ebc023bc88ff3724ba89312c44fb49be53dda","tid":981179,"uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"每次有Marvel戲上之前都會有依啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2063b51001e44caaef2c8bb7272302b10e244e9f","tid":981179,"uid":159183,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f94ebc023bc88ff3724ba89312c44fb49be53dda","tid":981179,"uid":212399,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"每次有Marvel戲上之前都會有依啲新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:56:54.000Z","msg":"係咪同avg3個篇新聞一樣<br />\n淨係將個3改做4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc0069d4adf02a5aefbc3c0d1a5e86333f4314c4","tid":981179,"uid":17678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T05:59:22.000Z","msg":"了咗佢心願可能死快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghe